bio:
With over 10 years experience in business development, management and consulting, Business Source Solutions has provided dedicated services to businesses across different industries.

Our consulting firm provides professional services focusing on building & growing profitable businesses.  We ensure that businesses implement strategies resulting in sustained delivery of goods/services resulting in higher profitability.  We are committed to assisting businesses with recurring revenue & maintaining the value of the products/services in the market.  We offer Business Operations Management, Strategic Planning & Business Coaching services.

We specialize in  planning and organizing a company for the purpose of accomplishing overall strategic and operational goals.  The areas of focus are: 
* Strategic Planning;
* Operations Management;
* Financial Planning & Monitoring;
* Marketing Plan Development & Execution;
* Information Technology;
* Human Resources Management.
